+
+<section class="card maintenance-boundary">
+<h2>Evidence and safety boundary</h2>
+<ul>
+<li>This page checks resources from the currently loaded website origin. It does not inspect the Git repository tree directly.</li>
+<li>This page cannot prove that GitHub Actions passed. Review the repository Actions page for workflow evidence.</li>
+<li>“Clear transient caches” removes only versioned runtime and JSON caches. It preserves reading lists, accessibility preferences and audio listening history.</li>
+<li>No production certification is claimed by this browser page or by a successful local check.</li>
+<li>A failed check may indicate deployment propagation, browser caching, network failure or a genuine missing resource; investigate before changing content.</li>
